{"tid":1408751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"提提大家正確七月化寶程序，唔係淨係燒紙皮","createTime":"2019-08-04T18:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T18:11:40.000Z","uid":285467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e1aec5c8600bdb7aea0a1e1205a3eae7bfab5712","tid":1408751,"uid":285467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:11:40.000Z","msg":"大家聽日入夜記得開始點做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1)\t最早於六時入夜後才化寶<br />\n2)\t最好選擇農曆七月三日至十四日化寶<br />\n3)\t一份街衣化寶通常有：觀音衣、元寶溪錢、金銀陰司紙、大悲咒及往生咒、七色彩紙、幽衣山祿、紅燭清香等，缺一不可<br />\n4)\t要將衣包完全燒盡才可<br />\n5)\t切勿踩到任何化寶及祭品<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/36868/%E7%9B%82%E8%98%AD%E7%AF%80-%E7%87%92%E8%A1%97%E8%A1%A3%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E5%8C%96-%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83%E8%A1%A3%E7%B4%99%E5%B8%83%E6%96%BD%E9%81%8A%E9%AD%82-%E5%86%80%E4%BF%9D%E9%A0%86%E5%88%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F36868%2F%25E7%259B%2582%25E8%2598%25AD%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E7%2587%2592%25E8%25A1%2597%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E5%258C%2596-%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2584%258F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E7%25B4%2599%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%2596%25BD%25E9%2581%258A%25E9%25AD%2582-%25E5%2586%2580%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%25A0%2586%25E5%2588%25A9&d=uztthH5CN7iuCFQPSeIHabc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=01a7c501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/36868/%E7%9B%82%E8%98%AD%E7%AF%80-%E7%87%92%E8%A1%97%E8%A1%A3%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E5%8C%96-%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83%E8%A1%A3%E7%B4%99%E5%B8%83%E6%96%BD%E9%81%8A%E9%AD%82-%E5%86%80%E4%BF%9D%E9%A0%86%E5%88%A9</a>"}]}